# Remember to never publicly share your keystore.
# See https://flutter.dev/to/reference-keystore
# The trailing * covers backup variants such as key.properties.release that
# preserve the previous release-signing config when we temporarily swap to a
# different keystore (e.g. debug keystore for Play developer verification).
key.properties*
**/*.keystore
**/*.jks

